@base = http://localhost:5173
@apiPrefix = /apis/examples.configbutler.ai/v1alpha1
@ns = demo
@session = kubecon-2026
@code = demo-join-code

### (1) Bootstrap device session + read session
GET {{base}}{{apiPrefix}}/namespaces/{{ns}}/quizsessions/{{session}}
X-Join-Code: {{code}}

### (2) Read session again (paste Cookie from response if not using a cookie jar)
GET {{base}}{{apiPrefix}}/namespaces/{{ns}}/quizsessions/{{session}}

### (3) Submit answers
POST {{base}}{{apiPrefix}}/namespaces/{{ns}}/quizsubmissions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiVersion": "examples.configbutler.ai/v1alpha1",
  "kind": "QuizSubmission",
  "metadata": {
    "generateName": "{{session}}-"
  },
  "spec": {
    "sessionRef": {
      "group": "examples.configbutler.ai",
      "kind": "QuizSession",
      "name": "{{session}}"
    },
    "submittedAt": "2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
    "answers": [
      { "questionId": "q1", "singleChoice": "Yes" },
      { "questionId": "q2", "multiChoice": ["Kubernetes", "Traefik"] },
      { "questionId": "q3", "number": 7 },
      { "questionId": "q4", "number": 42 },
      { "questionId": "q5", "freeText": "Loved it." }
    ]
  }
}
